	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Something I'm a little worried about.  If I have an explosion animation at 60fps that is 16 frames long, and lower it to 30fps and cut it down to 8 frames long, is it going to be noticeable?
<br />
<br />I might be able to make explosions be a "special case" where it breaks the engine's rules to add a little POW to it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
