<br />Probably due to a refresh rate mismatch between the GIF and your monitor. The game that uses these exact frames (it's for <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?t=6604" class="postlink">the NROM-128 compo</a>) looks fine on every TV I've tried it on, whether through an NES or through FCE Ultra GX on a Wii.

		

