	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That explosion makes me glad that I have 30fps to work with.
<br />
<br />I've always been an animation guy.  I do animation as a hobby all the time.  However my hobby of animation slows me down when programming games, because I have the habbit of drawing lots and lots of frames, and I have trouble getting all those frames to fit in v-ram or updating them fast enough.
<br />
<br />If you ever see me complain about the Snes's DMA being too slow or that it only uses 16 kB of memory for sprites, you'd know why.

		

